        "title": "The job hunt: hakemus, haastattelu, kokemus",
        "summary": "The words that get you hired: hakea (to apply), hakemus (application), työhaastattelu (job interview), kokemus (experience), palkka (salary). In speech a job is 'duuni' or 'paikka' - and the interview itself often decides how much kirjakieli you should mix in.",
