            "Mul on työhaastattelu torstaina. = I have a job interview on Thursday.",
            "Mul on aika paljon kokemusta asiakaspalvelusta. = I have quite a lot of customer service experience.",
            "Mä sain sen paikan! = I got the job!"
        ]
    },
